19-08-17T14:12:55.000Z","msg":"有無人知樓主咩背景?  <br />\n成日開有關日本po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82bac3c37d765e3e7710ea9aed2b212cfe849976","tid":1480810,"uid":147345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:22:20.000Z","msg":"想移，不過得廿萬，諗住過去讀書"},{"pid":"ef62b1dd93e104b48ecedb1ff3f26631d39907a3","tid":1480810,"uid":279963,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:23:32.000Z","msg":"我而家整理緊資料，希望由1982年中英談判開始，<br />\n講到今日點解我地要企出來以武力手段爭取民主<br />\n<br />\n要完成呢個list需要大家一齊去搵資料，<br />\n因為我一個人絕對冇辦法完成<br />\n(更新：已經完成左大約70%左右，多謝各位巴打絲打) <br />\n當中包括<br />\n1。一條相關新聞/wiki<br />\n2。一張相關照片<br />\n3。一段四~五句中文及/或英文簡介<br />\n<br />\n希望各位可以幫下我手入<br />\n去呢個google sheet入面將呢個list完成:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1c39ls77nUy_Vrr1mhIbduxIEpa7PkKRz2jZYI8hsJOA/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1c39ls77nUy_Vrr1mhIbduxIEpa7PkKRz2jZYI8hsJOA%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmrPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=38e08f32\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1c39ls77nUy_Vrr1mhIbduxIEpa7PkKRz2jZYI8hsJOA/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n切記，唔好整得太長，<br />\n唔好芝麻綠豆小事都擺入去<br />\n感謝各位幫忙<br />\n<br />\n我會將呢個list整成一套MEME<br />\n例子如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0BKFO0F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0BKFO0F.jpg&h=f2c7434b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前個list有：<br />\n1967\t六七暴動<br />\n1979\t香港前途問題<br />\n1984\t中英談判<br />\n1984\t中英聯合聲明<br />\n1988\t八八直選<br />\n1989\t天安門事件<br />\n1989\t天安門事件<br />\n1989\t天安門事件<br />\n1991\t九一直選<br />\n1992\t彭定康港督<br />\n1995\t臨時立法會<br />\n1996\t移民潮<br />\n1997\t中國收回香港<br />\n1997\t建華亂港<br />\n1997\t禽流感<br />\n1998\t胡仙案<br />\n1998\t亞洲金融風暴<br />\n1999\t居港權釋法<br />\n1999\t市政局解散<br />\n2001\t六七楊光暴動主腦獲頒大紫荊<br />\n2002\t高官問責制<br />\n2003\tSARS<br />\n2003\t廿三條立法<br />\n2003\t偷步買車<br />\n2003\t七一遊行<br />\n2003\t自由行政策<br />\n2004\t釋法否決07/08雙普選<br />\n2005\t領匯<br />\n2005\t老董腳痛落台<br />\n2006\t天星保育<br />\n2007\t皇后保育<br />\n2008\t社民連三子<br />\n2008\t以普通話教授中文科<br />\n2010\t反高鐵<br />\n2010\t香港交易所CEO由中國人接任，金融業被中國控制<br />\n2010\t五區公投<br />\n2010\t馬尼拉人質事件<br />\n2011\t民主黨接受政改方案<br />\n2012\t流浮山飯局<br />\n2012\t特首梁振英689票<br />\n2012\t國民教育<br />\n2012\t南丫島海難<br />\n2013\tHKTV不獲發牌<br />\n2014\t831框架<br />\n2014\t戴耀庭提議佔領中環<br />\n2014\t雨傘革命<br />\n2014\t暗角七警<br />\n2015\t銅鑼灣書店<br />\n2015\t否決政改<br />\n2016\t旺角魚蛋革命<br />\n2016\t梁天琦陳浩天被取消參選資格<br />\n2016\t多名當選議員被無理DQ<br />\n2017\t反一地兩檢<br />\n2017\t香港移交主權20周年<br />\n2018\t鄭若驊涉僭建<br />\n2018\tUGL 50M 事件放生<br />\n2019\t建議取消海外專科醫生於通過執業試才可於香港行醫"},{"pid":"ae006df36ef444b25add873cff263c0b66206825","tid":1480810,"uid":42393,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:09:21.000Z","msg":"留tg<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/goldenoptom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fgoldenoptom&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmrPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=6c40f7ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/goldenoptom</a>"},{"pid":"9841da350f3c0f3f68d42d3a87fdc69f259ab877","tid":1480810,"uid":99930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f147e30e7e4a450ca5c4ae6ef0fde5b8f1fe89e","tid":1480810,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:39:23.000Z","msg":"日本搵angel難唔難? 屋企人都諗住去做生意 再用working visa簽其他親戚過去"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:18:04.000Z","msg":"未入境就問手コキ<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1aade9ce892129b2e3dbafe41fcd71a3a8f7514","tid":1480810,"uid":283775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e4ea73504ff8a3823763e79b5836813e0ed31b1","tid":1480810,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60d01f5a8ef3b466c7982cc31716051fb9eef7cf","tid":1480810,"uid":283775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:52:22.000Z","msg":"屋企人移緊，但想搞生意嘅係我"},"citedBy":1,"r